text: Novonaryshevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnetroitsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 168 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Tuymazy, 7 km from Verkhnetroitskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Novonaryshevo
